Name: Average time from SW-EIC Accept to Awaiting Assignment to Batch
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-EIC Accept' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Total time between Manuscript Export Succeeded and Awaiting Assignment to Batch in variants that include SW-EIC Accept
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Minimum time it takes Awaiting Assignment to Batch to occur after First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Average duration of Awaiting Assignment to Batch when preceded by First Look-Your updates are overdue
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'First Look-Your updates are overdue' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Total time from SW-Reviewer Agreed (in any revision round) to Awaiting Assignment to Batch, considering only end-to-end accepted manuscripts
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Average time between SW-Reviewer Agreed and Awaiting Assignment to Batch across all process variants ending in acceptance
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Minimum time from the last occurrence of SW-Reviewer Agreed to Awaiting Assignment to Batch in multi-round review cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Total elapsed time between Revised Manuscript Submission Confirmation and Awaiting Assignment to Batch in variants where SW-Reviewer Agreed appears at least once
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Revised Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Time from the final decision activity (e.g., RW-EIC Accept) to Awaiting Assignment to Batch in accepted manuscripts
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'RW-EIC Accept' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Average time between the first SW-Reviewer Agreed and Awaiting Assignment to Batch in cases with multiple reviewer agreement events
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Total time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to Awaiting Assignment to Batch in variants that contain at least one SW-Reviewer Agreed event
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Minimum time between SW-Reviewer Agreed and the subsequent Manuscript Export Succeeded that directly precedes Awaiting Assignment to Batch
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Average waiting time to Awaiting Assignment to Batch after the completion of all revision-related activities following SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Total resolution time of Awaiting Assignment to Batch in process variants that originate from a major revision cycle initiated after SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'
